{"tid":617591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"撘過小巴 睇清蝻同蝗有乜分別","createTime":"2018-04-05T05:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T08:27:15.000Z","uid":50208,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"19c02d3599e28bd8f2ae57574e832575c3f386fb","tid":617591,"uid":50208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一啲分別都冇呀</span></span><br />\n聽住歌都聽到你地打扙咁傾計<br />\n堆細路又企住係櫈到左fing右fing<br />\n係左右都有fing呀屌你老母<br />\n佢地老豆老母又唔撚識叫翻佢地落離<br />\n係架小巴好似2個國家搞緊party<br />\n預先慶祝佔領香港咁款<br />\n當香港人冇撚到<br />\n<br />\n但有樣唔同嘅係<br />\nd蝻黎到香港起碼都肯學粵語<br />\n肯去用廣東話叫落車<br />\n你班仆街新移民唔係香港人排你<br />\n係你地自己跟本唔撚融入香港"},{"pid":"14534ef78cdac7e8f98910e8dceac788cf8a18bf","tid":617591,"uid":50208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T05:47:12.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e0813c72ed1a93d67df1ca119e8fa38bd56c9c25","tid":617591,"uid":100103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"啲蝻都係咁撚臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f43464c69e87869146e71ab1c63ffa30c4306e","tid":617591,"uid":50208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0813c72ed1a93d67df1ca119e8fa38bd56c9c25","tid":617591,"uid":100103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"啲蝻都係咁撚臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:12:18.000Z","msg":"每次同lift都好似要戴翻防毒面具"},{"pid":"831c27f656a2b5dafa6ecc0a2a001ae61411cd68","tid":617591,"uid":60831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:14:36.000Z","msg":"啲蝻亞大人本身就係垃圾，仲期望佢地會教仔??"},{"pid":"608e5071f5360700227f2c22e8cd6656cc1d37b6","tid":617591,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T06:46:45.000Z","msg":"蝻唔會俾d女做雞<br />\n呢點係我最憎！<br />\n蝗就起碼會生d靚女做雞俾我地呢d無女既毒男屌<br />\n叫做有得發洩下"},{"pid":"9